Juicer
The Juicer is a human who has voluntarily connected a drug-delivery harness to
their nervous system, flooding their body with combat stimulants that grant
incredible speed, strength, and reflexes: at the cost of a shortened lifespan.

Juicers cannot be de-juiced without dying (in most cases), and their lifespan
is roughly five years after conversion. What they gain: superhuman physical
attributes and some of the best combat skills in the game.

Attribute requirements: PS 9, PE 9.
Starting equipment: Juicer drug harness (fitted), light body armour, two ranged
weapons, vibro-knife, and one year of drug supply.
